Fidelity International Ltd, aBermuda-based investment advisory firm, and an affiliatedinvestment firm, American Values III N.V., said they haveacquired 208,000 share of Blasius Industries Inc.    In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission,the group said it bought the stake, which amounts to 5.3 pct ofthe total outstanding common stock, to acquire an equityinterest in the company for investment purposes.    The group said it may raise its stake or sell some or allof it, and has no plans to seek control of the company. Reuter&#3;